com.ibm.mobile.services.data

Class IBMUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.mobile.services.data.IBMDataObject
      • com.ibm.mobile.services.data.IBMUser

  • public class IBMUser
extends IBMDataObject
    IBMUser is a specialized object representing an end user. This class is a subclass of IBMDataObject. This class holds information about the user and provides methods for authenticating a user. For this version, the APIs are considered provisional. Developers should update their code accordingly as IBMUser moves closer to a finalized API
